      "text": "Section 6\nTransportation Appendix\nThis section is the \"what do we do now?\" transportation guide.\nUse it whenever you are moving between places and do not want to figure it out from scratch.\nGeneral Transportation Rules\nRule 1\nFor airports, leave earlier than feels necessary.\nThe extra buffer is better than stress.\nRule 2\nFor Amalfi Coast buses, verify timing the morning of travel.\nSummer traffic and full buses are normal.\nIf a bus is full, wait for the next one.\nRule 3\nFor short stressful connections, use Bolt, taxi, or private transfer .\nThis is a honeymoon, not a transportation challenge.\n1\n\nParis Transportation\nCharles de Gaulle Airport → Paris Airbnb\nUse\nOfficial airport taxi.\nDo Not Use\nA ride offered by someone approaching inside the terminal.\nSteps\nLand.\nPassport control.\nBaggage claim.\nCustoms.\nOptional ATM.\nFollow official taxi signs.\nTell driver:\nRue Sébastien Mercier\n75015 Paris\nExpected Cost\n€50–60\nExpected Time\n45–60 minutes\nParis Airbnb → Orly Airport\nUse\nBolt or taxi.\nPickup Time\n10:15 AM\n1. \n2. \n3. \n4. \n5. \n6. \n7. \n2\n\nDestination\nParis Orly Airport\nGoal Arrival\n11:00 AM\nWhy\nEasyJet bag drop opens at 11:15 AM and closes at 12:35 PM.\nVersailles Train Route\nParis → Versailles Château Rive Gauche\nUse Google Maps that morning.\nDestination:\nVersailles Château Rive Gauche\nArrival At Station\nAfter exiting:\nFollow signs for Château de Versailles.\nFollow the crowd.\nWalk approximately 10 minutes.\nLook for palace gates.\nNo taxi needed.\nNo shuttle needed.\nNaples Airport → Villa Gianlica\nUse\nVilla-arranged private transfer .\n1. \n2. \n3. \n4. \n3\n\nCost\n€190 total for two.\nDriver Needs\nProvide villa:\nFlight number\nArrival time\nPassenger names\nMobile phone number\nUpon Arrival\nCollect bags.\nExit arrivals.\nLook for driver sign.\nCheck phone/WhatsApp if driver is not immediately visible.\nCall villa contact if needed.\nVilla Gianlica Home Base\nAddress:\nVia Asciola 2\n84010 Praiano SA\nItaly\nMost local movements begin by walking toward the main road:\nVia Guglielmo Marconi / SS163\nVilla Gianlica → Positano\nUse\nSITA bus.\nDirection\nPositano / Sorrento-bound side of road.\n- \n- \n- \n- \n1. \n2. \n3. \n4. \n5. \n4\n\nBoard\nBus marked:\nPositano\nor\nSorrento\nExit\nSponda\nFrom Sponda\nWalk downhill toward:\nSpiaggia Grande\nReturn\nWalk back uphill to Sponda.\nBoard bus toward:\nPraiano / Amalfi\nExit near Villa Gianlica area.\nVilla Gianlica → Amalfi\nUse\nSITA bus.\nDirection\nAmalfi-bound side of road.\nBoard\nBus marked:\n5\n\nAmalfi\nExit\nAmalfi Bus Terminal\nThis is the main transfer hub.\nAmalfi → Bomerano\nFor Path of the Gods.\nAt Amalfi Bus Terminal\nLook for bus toward:\nAgerola / Bomerano\nAsk driver:\n\"Bomerano?\"\nExit\nBomerano\nTrail\nFollow signs toward:\nSentiero degli Dei\nPath of the Gods\nBomerano → Amalfi → Praiano\nReverse the route:\nBomerano bus stop\nBus to Amalfi\nAmalfi bus terminal\nBus toward Praiano / Positano\n1. \n2. \n3. \n4. \n6\n\nExit near Villa Gianlica\nVilla Gianlica → Marina di Praia\nUse for:\nFriday beach day\nMonday Capri boat day\nOption 1\nWalk if comfortable.\nOption 2\nUse taxi/local ride if hot, tired, or short on time.\nCapri Morning\nLeave villa:\n8:15 AM\nArrive Marina di Praia:\n8:45 AM\nMarina di Praia Notes\nThis is a small marina area.\nFor Capri day:\nLook for La Bellavita representative.\nHave booking number ready.\nIf confused, call +39 089 288 1694.\n5. \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n7\n\nVilla Gianlica → Moxy Pompeii\nUse villa-arranged private transfer .\nCost\n€160 total for two.\nTiming\nMorning transfer .\nPlan\nArrive Moxy.\nDrop luggage if room not ready.\nContinue to Pompeii.\nMoxy Pompeii → Pompeii Archaeological Park\nHotel\nMoxy Pompeii\nVia Castriota 43\nTorre Annunziata\nRecommended\nBolt or taxi.\nDestination\nPompeii Archaeological Park\nPorta Marina Entrance\nWhy\nSave energy for Pompeii itself.\nThe site is large, hot, and uneven.\n8\n\nMoxy Pompeii → Naples Airport\nUse\nBolt.\nMorning Plan\n5:45 AM wake up\n6:00 AM request Bolt\n6:15 AM depart hotel\n6:45–7:00 AM arrive airport\nBackup\nAsk Moxy front desk Tuesday evening to arrange taxi.\nAtlanta Airport → Woodstock\nAfter arrival:\nImmigration\nBaggage claim\nCustoms\nExit arrivals\nUse\nUber\nRecommendation\nRequest ride after bags are collected.\nDestination:\nWoodstock, Georgia\n1. \n2. \n3. \n4. \n9\n\nTransportation Stress Rule\nIf confused, tired, overheated, or carrying luggage:\nChoose the simplest paid option.\nThis trip already uses buses where it makes sense.\nFor luggage days and airport days, convenience wins.\n10",
