      "text": "Section 8\nPacking Guide, Ticket Tracker & Final Tips\nDaily Carry List\nBring every day:\n□ Phone\n□ Portable charger\n□ Credit card\n□ Some cash\n□ Sunglasses\n□ Sunscreen\n□ Water\n□ Passport photo saved on phone\n□ Comfortable shoes\nFlight Day Carry-On\nNever check:\n□ Passport\n□ Wallet\n□ Phone\n□ Phone charger\n1\n\n□ Portable charger\n□ Medications\n□ Headphones\n□ Travel documents\n□ One change of clothes\nParis Packing\nBring:\n□ Comfortable walking shoes\n□ Light jacket\n□ Small umbrella\n□ Crossbody bag or secure day bag\n□ Dress option for dinner\nAmalfi Coast Packing\nBring:\n□ Swimsuits\n□ Cover-up\n□ Sandals\n□ Sunscreen\n□ Sunglasses\n□ Casual dinner outfits\n□ Beach tote\n2\n\nCapri Boat Day Packing\nBring:\n□ Swimsuit\n□ Sunscreen\n□ Sunglasses\n□ Waterproof phone pouch\n□ Towel if desired\n□ Hat\nDo not bring:\n□ Outside food\n□ Outside drinks\n□ Large heavy bags\nPath of the Gods Packing\nBring:\n□ Sneakers\n□ Water\n□ Hat\n□ Sunscreen\n□ Light clothing\nDo not bring:\n□ Heavy backpack\n3\n\n□ Beach bag\n□ Uncomfortable sandals\nPompeii Packing\nBring:\n□ Sneakers\n□ Water\n□ Hat\n□ Portable charger\n□ Sunglasses\nRemember:\nPompeii is large, hot, uneven, and has limited shade.\nTicket Tracker\nAlready Booked\n✅ Delta flights\n✅ EasyJet flight\n✅ Wedding night Airbnb\n✅ Paris Airbnb\n✅ Seine Champagne Cruise\n✅ Big Bus Paris\n✅ Villa Gianlica\n✅ Cooking Class\n4\n\n✅ Capri Boat Tour\n✅ Moxy Pompeii\nStill Needs Booking\n□ Eiffel Tower Summit\n□ Louvre timed entry\n□ Versailles Passport with late Palace entry\nPending Details\n□ Exact Paris Airbnb street number\n□ Paris lockbox instructions\n□ Capri final boarding instructions\n□ Cooking class time confirmation\nFinal Week Checklist\nSeven days before departure:\n□ Screenshot all confirmations\n□ Save documents to both phones\n□ Confirm Uber to ATL\n□ Confirm villa transfer details\n□ Confirm ticket bookings\n□ Confirm dining reservations if desired\n□ Check weather\n5\n\n□ Pack chargers and adapters\n48-Hour Checklist\n□ Screenshot Paris Airbnb lockbox instructions\n□ Confirm Capri meeting point\n□ Confirm cooking class time\n□ Charge portable batteries\n□ Download offline maps if desired\n□ Review airport transportation plan\nDay-Of Travel Rules\nAirport Days\nLeave early.\nEat after security.\nKeep passports accessible.\nBoat Days\nExpect sea conditions to affect plans.\nBlue Grotto is never guaranteed.\nAmalfi Bus Days\nBe patient.\nBuses can be full.\n6\n\nTraffic can slow everything down.\nHike Day\nTurn around whenever you want.\nThe goal is the view, not completing the trail.\nPompeii Day\nDo not try to see everything.\nThree to four hours is enough.\nFinal Travel Tips\nMoney\nCarry some cash.\nUse cards where accepted.\nKeep a backup card separate.\nPhones\nCharge every night.\nCarry portable battery on long days.\nUse WhatsApp for local contacts if needed.\nSafety\nUse normal city awareness.\nKeep phones secure in Paris.\n7\n\nAvoid leaving bags unattended.\nDo not accept unofficial airport rides.\nThe Honeymoon Rule\nWhen choosing between:\nSqueezing in one more thing\nSitting somewhere beautiful together\nChoose sitting somewhere beautiful.\nThis trip is not a checklist.\nThis trip is the beginning of your marriage.\nProtect the memories.\nProtect the mood.\nProtect the magic.\n- \n- \n8",
